        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:4:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/4/1",
        "text": [
          ": \"رَكْعَتَانِ يُصَلِّيهِمَا مُتَزَوِّجٌ أَفْضَلُ مِنْ سَبْعِينَ رَكْعَةً يُصَلِّيهِمَا أَعْزَبُ \"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.4346 - Abdullah ibn Maymun narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) (peace be upon them), who said:\n\"Two units of prayer performed by a married person are better than seventy units of prayer performed by an unmarried person.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2830,
        "local_index": 2,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "4347 "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "-"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:4:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/4/2",
        "text": [
          " وَ قَالَ اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"لَرَكْعَتَانِ يُصَلِّيهِمَا مُتَزَوِّجٌ أَفْضَلُ مِنْ رَجُلٍ عَزَبٍ يَقُومُ لَيْلَهُ وَ يَصُومُ نَهَارَهُ \"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.4347 - The Prophet (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"Two units of prayer performed by a married person are better than an unmarried man who spends his nights in prayer and his days fasting.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
