        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:4:3",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/4/3",
        "text": [
          ": \"إِنَّ أَرَاذِلَ مَوْتَاكُمُ اَلْعُزَّابُ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.4348 - It is narrated that the Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said: \"Indeed, the most despicable of your dead are the unmarried.\""
          ]
        }
      },
