        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:4:4",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/4/4",
        "text": [
          ": \"أَكْثَرُ أَهْلِ اَلنَّارِ اَلْعُزَّابُ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.4349 - It has been narrated that the Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace and blessings be upon him and his family) said: \"The majority of the inhabitants of the Fire are the unmarried.\""
          ]
        }
      }
